# Intuition
Traverse the list and swap pairs of nodes one by one.
# Approach
![53a7a769-ce39-4d7d-9e37-cd0420f72bf0_1644988593.5987253.jpeg](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/1c079065-d5e5-478f-80bb-c20f4881d340_1684253393.321737.jpeg)


# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(N)(where n is number of nodes in the linked list)

- Space complexity:
O(1)-> since we are just changing the value of the nodes by swapping so no extra space is used.

# Code
```
/**
